             was indicted for <rs id="t18000219-80-off482" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18000219-80-off482" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18000219-80-off482" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18000219-80-cd483" type="crimeDate">31st of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000219-80-off482 t18000219-80-cd483"></join>, a deal box, value 5s. and one hundred and fifty pounds weight of thread, value 20l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18000219-80-victim736" type="victimName">
                     Andrew 
                     M'Whirter
